{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, M 1 undergoes re-evaluation on D 0 to create new trajectories T 1 = {τ ′ 1, τ ′ 2,.",
    "These trajectories, alongside T 0, undergo a filtering and merging process based on action knowledge.",
    "This refined set of trajectories is then utilized to fine-tune the model, resulting in an improved version, M 2.",
    "We continue iterating until the performance improvement on M test becomes small, at which point we halt the iteration process.",
    "Knowledge-Based Trajectory Filtering and Merging."
  ]
}